<item>
            <title>[FLINK-36815] series bugs of DSv2</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-36815</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I found four bugs in DSv2.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;1. The DSv2 &lt;em&gt;org.apache.flink.datastream.api.ExecutionEnvironment#fromSource&lt;/em&gt; method return a&#160;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;em&gt;NonKeyedPartitionStream&lt;/em&gt;, which does not allow users to set source configurations, such as operator name or parallelism.&lt;br/&gt;
2. The &lt;em&gt;org.apache.flink.datastream.api.context.TaskInfo&lt;/em&gt; lack &lt;em&gt;sub&lt;/em&gt;&lt;em&gt;taskIndex&lt;/em&gt; and &lt;em&gt;attemptNumber&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;3. The &lt;em&gt;open&lt;/em&gt; and &lt;em&gt;close&lt;/em&gt; methods of &lt;em&gt;org.apache.flink.datastream.api.function.ProcessFunction&lt;/em&gt; are not being called.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;4. The &lt;em&gt;open&lt;/em&gt; method of &lt;em&gt;org.apache.flink.datastream.api.function.ProcessFunction&lt;/em&gt; lacks relevant information, such as the current TaskInfo.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
